Output docs/media/clustering-deep-dive.gif

Set Shell "bash"
Set FontSize 14
Set Width 1100
Set Height 720
Set Padding 10
Set Margin 0
Set Theme "Catppuccin Mocha"
Set TypingSpeed 35ms
Set PlaybackSpeed 1.0

Hide
Type "clear" Enter
Show

Sleep 500ms
Type "# Show holes + safety + architectural notes for the notify fixture"
Sleep 400ms
Enter
Type "bin/phpdup analyze tests/Fixtures/notify --plain --min-impact=0"
Sleep 400ms
Enter
Sleep 8s
